<!-- slide -->

## **Recursive** Function

```scss
@function color(
  $name,
  $map: $colors
) {
  $name: map-get($map, $name) or $name;

  // Self-calling lookup
  @if map-has-key($colors, $name) {
    $name: color($name);
  }

  @return $name;
}
```

